fields.name: Huntsman V2 TKL
fields.description: Unrivalled responsiveness has never looked this lean. Meet the Razer Huntsman V2 TKL—a tenkeyless optical gaming keyboard with improved acoustics, near-zero input latency, and other high-end features to ensure a compact form factor geared for full-sized performance.

fields.name: Apex Pro TKL
fields.description: With the SteelSeries Apex Pro gaming keyboard (without numeric keypad), you easily dominate any battlefield. This mechanical beast relentlessly hunts down all your enemies without blinking its dimly lit buttons. Go into battle to win!

fields.name: Viper V2 Pro
fields.description: The Viper V2 PRO from Razer is the successor to the award-winning Razer Viper Ultimate. It's one of the lightest wireless gaming mice ever, and it's been upgraded in every way for increased performance.

fields.name: G Pro X
fields.description: The Logitech G Pro X Superlight wireless gaming mouse comes with a fantastic Hero sensor with up to 25600 DPI resolution, 400 IPS speed, 1 ms response time and the same design as a standard G Pro but with 25% less weight.

fields.name: G305
fields.description: Whether you're a gamer who demands the very best performance or you simply want a mouse that doesn't weigh you down, the G305 Lightspeed Wireless Gaming Mouse from Logitech is the perfect choice. This wireless gaming mouse is designed for serious gamers, with the latest technological innovations and an impressive battery life of 250 hours.

fields.name: G815
fields.description: The G815 is a high-performance gaming keyboard that suits you who want a solid keyboard for gaming or work. You can choose between approximately 16.8 million colors on each key so you can find the right lighting for you. In addition to being equipped with advanced technology, the G815 is also very robust with its durable design.

fields.name: Arctis 9
fields.description: Arctis 9 Wireless - from the creators of the most award-winning headset series in gaming history - combines lossless, wireless 2.4GHz low-latency audio with simultaneous Bluetooth audio for wireless performance everywhere.

fields.name: H1
fields.description: Made for the highest level of esports, the H1 headset is designed to bring you supreme comfort, durability and the perfect soundscape for gaming.

fields.name: MZ1
fields.description: The Xtrfy MZ1 is designed by one of the world's top gaming mouse testers, Zy “Rocket Jump Ninja” Rykoa. It has a Pixart 3389 sensor, RGB lighting and weighs only 56 grams.

fields.name: Titan Evo
fields.description: The best from Secretlab OMEGA 2020 and TITAN 2020. Now collected in one gaming chair. The Secretlab TITAN Evo 2022 combines several of our proprietary technologies and design innovations for a new level of custom support and performance. This is award-winning comfort. Now further developed.

fields.name: Vernazza
fields.description: Vernazza is one of Arozzi's top chairs with all the best features built into a comfortable chair. From the super soft headrest cushion to the ergonomic design, Vernazzan will ensure that long hours of computing are done in maximum comfort.

fields.name: Verona V2
fields.description: The new gaming chair Verona V2 in black edition from Arozzi with even more settings so that you get the ergonomic support needed for long gaming sessions.

fields.name: Tarok Pro X
fields.description: Sit comfortably while gaming with the Razer Tarok Pro X gaming chair, which features 3D padded armrests and also durable upholstery and a lockable recline mechanism. For more comfort, it is also equipped with memory foam pillows.

fields.name: Nari Essential
fields.description: The Razer Nari is a wireless gaming headset with high comfort and THX Spatial Audio that delivers the next generation of virtual surround sound. The wireless frequency of 2.4 GHz allows you to enjoy incredible and lag-free performance. Nari Essential has a battery life of a full 16 hours. The oval ear pads containing cooling gel reduce heat build-up so you can play comfortably even during long gaming sessions.

fields.name: Cloud Alpha
fields.description: The HyperX Cloud Alpha Wireless gaming headset has a battery life of up to 300 hours, HyperX dual-chamber elements and a noise-cancelling microphone. Compatible with DTS® Headphone:X® with spatial sound.

fields.name: Cloud Stinger Core
fields.description: The HyperX Cloud Stinger Core is specifically designed for PC gamers looking for a lightweight gaming headset with excellent sound quality. It has everything you need as a gamer: smooth and reliable with excellent sound quality while sitting comfortably.

fields.name: Nitro N50-640
fields.description:
The Nitro 50 gaming PC in black metal with fiery decor is the fuel you need for lag-free high-frame-rate gaming sessions. Turn up the settings to the max!

Specs:
Core: Intel i5-12400F
RAM: 8GB DDR4
Graphics: Nvidia GeForce GTX1650 4GB
Hard drive: 1 SSD 512 GB
Motherboard: Intel B660

fields.name: Rog Strix GL10
fields.description:
GL10 delivers great gaming experiences and is powered by AMD Ryzen CPU and NVIDIA® GeForce graphics. 802.11ac Gigabit Wi-Fi provides high speeds and a stable wireless Internet connection, high-performance M.2 PCIe SSD provides faster storage performance.

Specs:
Core: AMD Ryzen 5 3400G
RAM: 16GB DDR4
Graphics: Nvidia GeForce GTX1660TI 6GB
Hard drive: 1 SSD 512 GB
Motherboard: AMD B550

fields.name: Predator Orion 7000
fields.description:
Show off your new powerful gaming PC and let it light up your room in multiple colors with the help of ARGB lighting on the powerful FrostBlade fans that spin in time with the infinite high-speed harmony and cool the powerful hardware.

Specs:
Core: Intel i7-12700K
RAM: 32GB DDR5
Graphics: Nvidia GeForce RTX3080 10GB
Hard drive: 1 TB SSD
Motherboard: Acer Z690

fields.name: Rog Strix G15DK
fields.description:
ROG Strix G15DK is designed for superior gameplay with top-class cooling, this compact gaming PC uses an NVIDIA® GeForce RTX 3070 graphics card and an AMD Ryzen™ 7-5800X processor to deliver high frame rates and performance.

Specs:
Core: AMD Ryzen 7 5800X
RAM: 16GB DDR4
Graphics: Nvidia GeForce RTX3070 8GB
Hard drive: 1 SSD 512 GB
Motherboard: AMD B550

fields.name: TUF Dash F15
fields.description: ASUS TUF Dash F15 is a powerful gaming laptop with 15.6" FHD IPS screen (144 Hz), Intel Core i511300H processor, 16 GB RAM, 512 GB SSD, NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3060 graphics, WiFi 6, Thunderbolt 4 and Windows 10 .

fields.name: Rog Flow X13
fields.description: Powerful gaming computer from ASUS with GeForce RTX 3050 graphics card and Ryzen 9 5900HS processor that will give you a perfect gaming experience everywhere.

fields.name: Blade 15 Advanced
fields.description: A critically acclaimed gaming laptop with more powerful GeForce® 30 series graphics, the latest Intel processor and the sharpest QHD display, RGB lighting, all packed into the world's thinnest 15-inch gaming chassis.

fields.name: Blade 17 Pro
fields.description: This powerful laptop pushes the boundaries of what a gaming laptop can do. The Razer Blade Pro 17 is built with a powerful processor and a maxed-out graphics card to run performance-demanding AAA games on the fly.

fields.name: VG246H
fields.description: ASUS VG246H is a 23.8" IPS computer monitor with FHD resolution and 1 ms response time. This gaming monitor is compatible with AMD FreeSync and can be turned, tilted, rotated and adjusted in height.

fields.name: Optix G27C4
fields.description: The MSI Optix G27C4 is a 27" curved computer monitor with FHD resolution (1920 x 1080), VA panel, 165 Hz refresh rate and 1 ms response time. This gaming monitor is also compatible with AMD FreeSync technology for smooth and responsive gaming graphics.

fields.name: Odyssey G7
fields.description: Odyssey stands out in the category by mixing the gaming experience with a mix of futuristic design and technology. Thanks to contrasting elements such as color, shape and lines with a minimalist design, the Odyssey monitor breathes raw strength.

fields.name: Predator XB323QUNV
fields.description: ACER Predator XB323 QUNV is a 31.5" computer monitor with WQHD resolution (2560 x 1440), IPS panel, 170 Hz refresh rate and 1 ms response time. This gaming monitor is also compatible with FreeSync Premium technology for smooth and responsive game graphics.

fields.name: Rog Strix XG49VQ
fields.description: ROG Strix XG49VQ is a 49-inch 32:9 (3840 x 1080) super ultra-wide HDR gaming monitor HDR with 144 Hz refresh rate and support for FreeSync 2 for silky smooth framerates. Smart picture-in-picture functions and many connections for game consoles and computer.

fields.name: Odyssey Neo G9
fields.description: Samsung Odyssey G9 (S49AG950) is a 49" computer monitor with DQHD resolution (5120 x 1440), VA panel, 240 Hz frame rate and 1 ms response time and HDR10+. This gaming monitor is also compatible with AMD FreeSync and G-Sync -technique.

fields.name: G Pro
fields.description: Built for the pros, inside and out. With its compact design without a numeric keypad, the Logitech G PRO mechanical gaming keyboard frees up table space for low-sensitivity mouse movements. Professional-grade Clicky switches provide audible feedback.

fields.name: G413
fields.description: The G413 backlit mechanical gaming keyboard delivers unmatched performance, technology and functionality in a balanced design. Featuring Romer-G™ switches, the G413 provides outstanding speed, responsiveness and durability.
